The circumstances surrounding Balaji's death are still under investigation, and authorities have stated that it appears to be a suicide. However, Balaji's family and friends have expressed concerns about the circumstances leading up to his death, as well as the timing and location of his passing. Balaji's death has highlighted the importance of protecting the rights of whistleblowers and ensuring their safety and well-being.
